This paper deals with intrusion detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also employs machine learning techniques, specifically SVMs, which are commonly used in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of fine-grained recognition protocols, which may involve image or signal processing techniques commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV).
